msgid "Deploy vLLM-Ascend with MindIE-Motor"
msgstr "使用MindIE-Motor部署vLLM-Ascend"

#: ../../source/user_guide/deployment_guide/using_mindie_motor.md:3
msgid "1. Overview"
msgstr "1.概述"

#: ../../source/user_guide/deployment_guide/using_mindie_motor.md:5
msgid ""
"[MindIE-Motor](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-PyMotor) provides one-click"
" deployment for **prefill–decode (PD) disaggregation** and **PD "
"aggregation** on Ascend NPUs with vLLM-Ascend. It uses **high-performance "
"scheduling and load balancing**, together with **RAS (Reliability, "
"Availability and Serviceability) capabilities**, to build inference services"
" that are fast and highly stable."
msgstr ""
"[MindIE-Motor](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/MindIE-PyMotor)为Ascend NPU上的vLLM-"
"Ascend提供**prefill–decode "
"(PD)分离**和**PD聚合**的一键部署。它采用**高性能调度和负载均衡**，结合**RAS（可靠性、可用性和可服务性）能力**，构建快速且高度稳定的推理服务。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/deployment_guide/using_mindie_motor.md:7
msgid "2. Getting Started"
msgstr "2.快速开始"

#: ../../source/user_guide/deployment_guide/using_mindie_motor.md:9
msgid ""
